{"tid":1115482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百國泰乘客被困機艙5粒鐘　僅獲餐包曲奇頂肚","createTime":"2019-04-19T08:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T09:49:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1078bae18731ef5890ee5fac7db1b547fee4f1","tid":1115482,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜排名節節下跌的國泰航空</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一班向逾百乘客復活節「贈興」。國泰航班CX347原定今日(19日)早上10時由北京返香港，惟其後以多個原因，包括航空管制、飛機漏油及香港天氣轉差為由數度延遲，直至今日下午3時30分仍未能起飛。東網正等候國泰的回覆。<br />\n<br />\n最離譜是國泰不讓乘客返回登機閘口，要他們困在機艙內5個小時，期間未有提供飛機餐，僅提供一個餐包及一塊曲奇讓乘客充饑，有受影響乘客批評國泰的安排極差，猶如要乘客在狹窄的機艙內困獸鬥，完全不理會乘客的感受，「再係咁delay(延誤)，我歐洲都返來啦！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190419/bkn-20190419153959388-0419_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190419%2Fbkn-20190419153959388-0419_00822_001.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=1d671cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190419/bkn-20190419153959388-0419_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b53f99611d85f3d842ff65dfec60be9736940ef7","tid":1115482,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bb10a8d38ffa2dc289001d535adaa8d453582ac","tid":1115482,"uid":99700,"like":18,"dislike":26,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"國泰係仆街,但好人好者都唔去北京啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ba751bd3b399e4357cedd6999b68b84e92740f","tid":1115482,"uid":174432,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"蝗國delay唔係正常事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過幾次未試過準時"},{"pid":"f17b16b390ecb0f30720b22096f4a131df188762","tid":1115482,"uid":49316,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"北京上機等五粒鐘真係平常事<br />\n<br />\n知道今日天氣差 改佐機票尋晚返。原本八點機 凌晨兩點半到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3176a6f05865a6243832df6d42d2939e61fde7","tid":1115482,"uid":22913,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"餐包曲奇算係咁啦<br />\n比碗翅你食好無"},{"pid":"a9a4af4e7e171a54886de4e730d45dd99d09adb1","tid":1115482,"uid":35231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"返gate？重新再排過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294e5d23172849466eafd317cabc3ba08c33344d","tid":1115482,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"支那北京空管先係禍首喎"},{"pid":"de24953553d81e2926fb11b569fa26a48ebf0bdd","tid":1115482,"uid":22422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"一見國泰 個腦即刻彈個「因」字出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670fb7792f66b9fbaafb4e9577fa731fe36a5607","tid":1115482,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:57:41.000Z","msg":"delay係咁㗎啦 有嘢俾你食仲想點<br />\n空姐都陪你一齊餓"},{"pid":"aee4234e27a34e7fa8bbe82f60902582da3ebf9c","tid":1115482,"uid":55846,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"講真第一日先知大陸空管delay咩？ 平心而論咪入因航數<br />\n<br />\n又話唔比你地落機等，你以為架機ready 左即刻叫你上機就走得？調番轉係要架機ready先比你排隊take off，你估airline 好想delay？ 佢分分鐘架機等住飛第二到仲驚過你。"},{"pid":"9712ffae726e8bc1f395742d3b906e3b47d96620","tid":1115482,"uid":29400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"CX347用333點解唔比返KA做，真係多客個陣先濕租CX777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4a271d55daa9596d74ba11812e7aa9fd6d9505","tid":1115482,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislik